Odaily Planet Daily News According to Ai Yi, an analyst on the chain, the address that spent $16.41 million to build positions in PNUT, ai16z and arc in the past three months is likely to belong to Galaxy Digital. At present, the agency's cumulative losses on these three Memecoins are as high as $8.493 million, including: 
PNUT: 21.46 million pieces, cost $0.3743, floating loss of $4.935 million; 
ai16z: 7.53 million pieces, cost $0.7446, floating loss of $3.133 million; 
arc: All recharged into Gate yesterday, cost $0.2913, loss of $425,000, it is not yet certain whether it participated in market making.

Odaily Planet Daily News According to Ai Yi, an analyst on the chain, in the past 4 hours, two whales have deposited 5,800 ETH to the exchange, worth $15.73 million.
Address 0xc8D...Be2CD sold 3,100 ETH opened at an average price of $1,890 in April 2023, and if sold, it will make a profit of $2.546 million;
Address 0x41A...F7277 sold 2,700 ETH withdrawn from the exchange at a high of $3,499 eight months ago, and if sold, it will lose $1.655 million.
